title: Dundee Corporation Announces Voting Results for Election of Directors
text:
July 24, 2015 17:01 ET Dundee Corporation Announces Voting Results for Election of Directors 
TORONTO, ONTARIO--(Marketwired - July 24, 2015) - In accordance with regulatory requirements, Dundee Corporation (TSX:DC.A) ("Dundee") announces that at the recently held annual meeting of shareholders (the "Meeting"), all of the nominees for election as directors of Dundee referred to in its management information circular for the Meeting were elected by way of show of hands.
